<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'About' }) %>

<main class="container">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <h1>About Action Jackson Installs</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Professional networking solutions for Columbia, Missouri and surrounding areas</p>
  </div>

  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="intro-content">
      <h2>Your Local Networking Experts</h2>
      <p>Action Jackson Installs is a locally owned and operated networking installation company serving Columbia, Missouri and the surrounding Mid-Missouri region. Founded on the principles of reliability, technical expertise, and exceptional customer service, we've built our reputation by delivering professional-grade networking solutions for both residential and business clients.</p>
      
      <p>As a local business, we understand the unique needs of our community. Whether you're a homeowner looking to upgrade your home network, a small business requiring reliable connectivity, or a larger organization needing comprehensive networking infrastructure, we bring the same level of professionalism and precision to every project.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-overview">
    <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Network Installation</h3>
        <p>Professional setup and configuration of routers, switches, and networking equipment for optimal performance and reliability.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-tools"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Cable Management</h3>
        <p>Clean, organized cable routing and infrastructure installation that looks professional and maintains signal integrity.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Security Systems</h3>
        <p>Installation and configuration of security cameras, access points, and monitoring equipment for complete peace of mind.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Device Configuration</h3>
        <p>Expert setup of computers, tablets, phones, and smart devices to work seamlessly with your network infrastructure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-choose-us">
    <h2>Why Choose Action Jackson Installs?</h2>
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Professional Excellence</h3>
        <p>We bring technical expertise and professional standards to every installation, ensuring your network performs reliably for years to come.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Reliable Service</h3>
        <p>Punctuality and precision are our hallmarks. We show up on time, work efficiently, and complete projects when promised.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Local Commitment</h3>
        <p>As a Columbia-based business, we're invested in our community. Your success is our success, and we're here for ongoing support.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> Transparent Pricing</h3>
        <p>No surprises or hidden fees. Our online quote system provides upfront pricing so you know exactly what to expect.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-wrench"></i> Quality Equipment</h3>
        <p>We work with the latest networking hardware and cables, ensuring your installation meets current standards and future needs.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Ongoing Support</h3>
        <p>Our relationship doesn't end at installation. We're available for questions, troubleshooting, and future expansion needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-area">
    <h2>Serving Mid-Missouri</h2>
    <p>Based in Columbia, Missouri, we proudly serve the greater Mid-Missouri region including surrounding communities. Our local focus allows us to provide personalized service while maintaining the quick response times you need for both planned installations and urgent networking issues.</p>
    
    <div class="cta-section">
      <h3>Ready to Get Started?</h3>
      <p>Experience the Action Jackson difference for your next networking project.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/quotes" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
        <a href="/scheduling" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
.about-hero {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  padding: 2rem 0;
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--muted-color);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.about-intro {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.intro-content h2 {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.intro-content p {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.services-overview {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.services-overview h2 {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.service-card {
  background: var(--card-background-color);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border-color);
  transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.service-icon {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.service-card h3 {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.why-choose-us {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.why-choose-us h2 {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.benefits-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.benefit {
  padding: 1rem;
}

.benefit h3 {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.benefit h3 i {
  color: var(--primary);
  width: 1.2rem;
}

.service-area {
  background: var(--card-background-color);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border-color);
  text-align: center;
}

.service-area h2 {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.service-area p {
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.cta-section {
  margin-top: 2rem;
}

.cta-section h3 {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.cta-buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.btn {
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  background: var(--primary-hover, var(--primary));
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--primary);
  border-color: var(--primary);
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

/* Mobile responsiveness */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .services-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .benefits-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .btn {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 250px;
  }
}
</style>

